3.3 Configuration
AI ensembles use a central settings.json file:
{
  "paths": {
    "process_dir": "process",
    "template_dir": "sources/templates",
    "notebooks_dir": "notebooks"
  },
  "models": {
    "defaults": {
      "text": "claude-3-5-haiku",
      "experimental": "gemini-2-thinking",
      "audio": "whisper-large-v3"
    }
  }
}

4.5 Result Storage
Results are stored in JSON format with detailed metadata:
{
  "block_id": "analysis_1",
  "model": "gemini-2",
  "timestamp": "2024-02-15T14:30:00Z",
  "input": {
    "prompt": "Analyze this document...",
    "files": {
      "document": "path/to/source.txt"
    },
    "options": {
      "temperature": 0.1,
      "max_tokens": 8192
    }
  },
  "response": {
    "text": "Analysis results...",
    "tokens": 1250,
    "duration": 3.5,
    "model_version": "gemini-2-20240215"
  }
}

