5.3 Task Templates

5.3.1 1. Academic Analysis
{# templates/academic.j2 #}
Analyze the following {{DOCUMENT_TYPE}} in academic style:

Content:
{{CONTENT}}

Provide:
1. Methodological approach
2. Critical analysis
3. Supporting evidence
4. Scholarly context


5.3.2 2. Data Extraction
{# templates/extract.j2 #}
Extract information from this {{SOURCE_TYPE}}:

Source:
{{SOURCE}}

Required fields:
{{#each FIELDS}}
- {{this.name}}: {{this.description}}
{{/each}}

Format: {{OUTPUT_FORMAT}}

6.3 Process Directory
The process/ directory stores processing results and metadata:

6.3.1 1. Result Structure
{
  "notebook": "01-analysis.qmd",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "id": "block_1",
      "model": "claude-3-5-haiku",
      "input": {
        "files": {
          "document": "sources/documents/text.md"
        },
        "template": "analysis.j2",
        "variables": {
          "STYLE": "academic"
        }
      },
      "output": {
        "text": "Analysis results...",
        "metadata": {
          "tokens": 1250,
          "duration": 3.5
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}


6.3.2 2. Cache Organization
process/
├── cache/                    # Cached responses
│   ├── claude/              # By model
│   │   └── responses/
│   └── whisper/
│       └── transcripts/
├── metadata/                 # Processing metadata
└── results/                 # Final results

7.3 Configuration

7.3.1 Environment Setup
# Required environment variables
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-key"
export GOOGLE_API_KEY="your-key"
export GROQ_API_KEY="your-key"

# Optional settings
export AI_NOTEBOOK_CACHE_DIR="/path/to/cache"
export AI_NOTEBOOK_TEMPLATE_DIR="/path/to/templates"


7.3.2 Settings File
# settings.json
{
  "paths": {
    "process_dir": "process",
    "template_dir": "sources/templates",
    "notebooks_dir": "notebooks"
  },
  "models": {
    "defaults": {
      "text": "claude-3-5-haiku",
      "audio": "whisper-large-v3"
    }
  },
  "processing": {
    "parallel": true,
    "cache": true,
    "overwrite": false
  }
}
